== Usage ==
This template provides an external link to [[National Criminal Justice Reference Service]] (NCJRS) abstracts for publications and criminal justice journals.

This template uses one unnamed reference, the NCJ number:

{{markup
|<nowiki>{{NCJ|203876}}</nowiki>
|{{NCJ|203876}}
}}

To search for an article, goto http://www.ncjrs.gov/abstractdb/search.asp
<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- Categories and interwikis go here: -->
[[Category:External link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

{{Documentation subpage}}
{{tsh|NCJ}}
